 HoYoverse space fantasy RPG.\nHop aboard the Astral Express and experience the galaxy's infinite wonders filled with adventure and thrills.","effectiveDate":"2023-04-26T00:30:00.000Z","expiryDate":null,"viewableDate":"2023-02-10T02:00:00.000Z","allowPurchaseForPartialOwned":true,"offerType":"BASE_GAME","externalLinks":null,"isCodeRedemptionOnly":false,"keyImages":[{"type":"OfferImageWide","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-1iemn.jpg"},{"type":"OfferImageTall","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-1qdh6.jpg"},{"type":"Thumbnail","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-1qdh6.jpg"},{"type":"heroCarouselVideo","url":"com.epicgames.video.qs:\u002F\u002F59e05b0b-d99b-4cea-90fe-725c01d07ea4?cover=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.epicgames.com%2Fspt-assets%2F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5%2Fhonkai-star-rail-video-npkls.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-af11f.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-2jrv1.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-1oeqp.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-jmjqw.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-16aui.jpg"},{"type":"featuredMedia","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-3frk7.png"}],"longDescription":"\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Honkai Star Rail-1l9zj](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002F6f3979ff608f42e286c83507a69b27f5\u002Fhonkai-star-rail-1l9zj.png)\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# The brand-new Version 4.3 \"The Lethe Below the Living\" is now available!\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nNew Character: Mortenax Blade (Nihility: Fire)\nCharacter Rerun: Yao Guang (Elation: Physical), Cyrene (Remembrance: Ice), Phainon (Destruction: Physical)\nNew Story: Trailblaze Mission \"Planarcadia\" - \"The Lethe Below the Living\"\nNew Events: Pixel Plane Rumble, Wispae Amusement Park, and more\nOthers: New maps, new enemies, new stages, and more\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# □ Explore Distinct Worlds — Discover the boundless universe filled with wonder\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\n3, 2, 1, initiating warp! A space station with Curios sealed away, a foreign planet with an eternal winter, a starship hunting down abominations, the Planet of Festivities nested in sweet dreams, The Eternal Land where destiny hangs by a thread, the arcadia that had once fallen into a painting scroll... Every stop of the Astral Express is a never-before-seen view of the galaxy! Explore fantastical worlds and civilizations, uncover mysteries beyond imagination, and set out on a journey of wonder!\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# □ Riveting RPG Experience — A best-in-class immersive adventure beyond the stars\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nEmbark on a galactic adventure where you shape the story. Our cutting-edge engine renders high-quality cinematics in real-time, our innovative facial expression system concocts genuine sentiments, and HOYO-MiX's original score sets the stage. Join us now and journey through a universe of conflict and collaboration, where your choices define the outcome!\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# □ Fateful Encounters Await! — Cross paths with characters intertwined by destiny\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nAs you traverse the sea of stars, you'll not only have countless adventures, but also many chance encounters. You will forge friendships in a frozen land, fight side by side with comrades in the Xianzhou crisis, and have unexpected encounters in a golden dream. A game of an Aeon when the Phantasmoon waxes full... On this alien world, you will meet greet companions walking these different paths amongst the starts and experience incredible journeys together. Let your laughter and woes compose the story of your present, past, and future.\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# □ Turn-based Combat Reimagined — Exhilarating multifaceted gameplay fueled by strategy and skill\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nEngage in a combat system that sports a variety of team compositions. Match your lineups based on your enemy's qualities and strike while the iron is hot to bring down your foes and claim victory! Break Weaknesses! Deliver Follow-up Attacks! Deal Damage over Time... and try out the brand-new Aha Instant! Countless strategies and tactics await your unlocking. Build an approach suited for you and face the onrush of successive challenges! Beyond the thrilling turn-based combat, there are also simulation management modes, casual elimination mini-games, puzzle exploration, and more... Explore an exciting variety of gameplay and experience endless possibilities!\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# □ Top-Tier Voice Actors for an Immersive Experience — A dream team of multiple language dubs assembled for the entire story\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nWhen words come alive, when stories give you a choice, when characters possess a soul... We present to you dozens of emotions, hundreds of facial expressions, thousands of lore pieces, and a million words that make up this universe's beating heart. With full voice-over in four languages, the characters will transcend their virtual existences and become your tangible companions, creating a new chapter in this tale together with you.\n","seller":{"id":"o-wlaqew5gv79ufa3slnqhhsqbpjdvnb","name":"COGNOSPHERE PTE. LTD."},"productSlug":"honkai-star-rail","publisherDisplayName":"COGNOSPHERE PTE. LTD.","releaseDate":"2023-04-26T00:30:00.000Z","urlSlug":"honkai-star-rail","url":null,"tags":[{"id":"29088","name":"Online Multiplayer","groupName":"feature"},{"id":"21121","name":"Great for Quick Sessions","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21122","name":"Diverse Characters","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"1188","name":"RELAXING","groupName":null},{"id":"9547","name":"Windows","groupName":"platform"},{"id":"9549","name":"Controller Support","groupName":"feature"},{"id":"21134","name":"Beautiful Visuals","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21138","name":"Recommend this Game","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21139","name":"Amazing Characters","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21140","name":"Amazing Storytelling","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21141","name":"Extremely Fun","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"1367","name":"RPG","groupName":"genre"},{"id":"21147","name":"Inclusive Character Customization","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"1117","name":"Adventure","groupName":"genre"},{"id":"21149","name":"Quickly Understand the Controls","groupName":"usersay"},{"id":"21119","name":"Great for Beginners","groupName":"usersay"}],"items":[{"id":"c1d9ac6e15ea40e1bd64e2f91fd98d87","namespace":"a2dcbb9e34204bda9da8415f97b3f4ea","releaseInfo":[]}],"customAttributes":[{"key":"autoGeneratedPrice","value":"false"},{"key":"isManuallySetViewableDate","value":"true"},{"key":"isPromotionalContentUsed","value":"false"},{"key":"publisherName","value":"COGNOSPHERE PTE. LTD."},{"key":"developerName","value":"Shanghai miHoYo HaiYuancheng Technology Co., Ltd"},{"key":"com.epicgames.app.productSlug","value":"honkai-star-rail"},{"key":"isBlockchainUsed","value":"false"}],"categories":[{"path":"games"},{"path":"games\u002Fedition"},{"path":"games\u002Fedition\u002Fbase"},{"path":"applications"}],"c