k: Drowning On Dry Land-1fmjk](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-1fmjk.gif)\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-zsiq6](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-zsiq6.gif)\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-1bwrd](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-1bwrd.gif)\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# From The Team\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nSome time ago we were lucky enough to get some funds from a government grant to work on a video game prototype. After a lot of work that initial prototype has turned into this. It's a small game that has allowed the team to explore so many ideas we never could have otherwise. It was made with a lot of heart and love that couldn't exist without this institution:\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-xkkn1](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-xkkn1.png)\n","seller":{"id":"o-u4quu47t6b775rggwhmfjfg8qlektp","name":"My Next Games"},"productSlug":null,"publisherDisplayName":"My Next Games","releaseDate":"2026-05-06T16:00:00.000Z","urlSlug":"9a12b7b988a04791b88c86a5b2eea989","url":null,"tags":[{"id":"1395","name":"Narration","groupName":"genre"},{"id":"33639","name":"Promotional Content","groupName":null},{"id":"19847","name":"Achievements","groupName":"epicfeature"},{"id":"1336","name":"Action-Adventure","groupName":"genre"},{"id":"1370","name":"Single Player","groupName":"feature"},{"id":"9547","name":"Windows","groupName":"platform"},{"id":"29899","name":"Deals of the Week","groupName":"event"},{"id":"1263","name":"Indie","groupName":"genre"}],"items":[{"id":"bdffc3b2db6f43f9b355a67e6dbe8956","namespace":"68d6947f4d0a4ffc88670360