ts\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-1just.png"}],"longDescription":"\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# Hand-Crafted Indie Game\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nAn adventure game inspired by your favorite dark saturday morning cartoons! (The runtime is only around thirty minutes as well. Pretend it’s a feature.)\n\nThe time-traveling vigilante Hank thought he was going for a nice drink, only to find himself poisoned! Paralyzed, he lies on the floor, drowning in a puddle of spilled beer. As his brain withers away, the hero embarks on a journey through his own subconscious. Will he find something there that can save him?\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-1fmjk](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-1fmjk.gif)\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-zsiq6](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-zsiq6.gif)\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-1bwrd](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-1bwrd.gif)\n\n\u003C!--textBlock--\u003E\n\u003C!--title--\u003E\n# From The Team\n\u003C!--text--\u003E\nSome time ago we were lucky enough to get some funds from a government grant to work on a video game prototype. After a lot of work that initial prototype has turned into this. It's a small game that has allowed the team to explore so many ideas we never could have otherwise. It was made with a lot of heart and love that couldn't exist without this institution:\n\n\u003C!--image--\u003E\n![Hank: Drowning On Dry Land-xkkn1](https:\u002F\u002Fcdn1.epicgames.com\u002Fspt-assets\u002Ff3c1b731e7a845ee840bb8e318216183\u002Fhank-drowning-on-dry-land-xkkn1.png)\n","seller":{"id":"o-u4quu47t6b775rggwhmfjfg8qlektp","name":"My Next Games"},"product